Sample Bundles/Snap
===================

Simple samples to show how the pieces are wired together.

API is just that, independent of the implementation and Snap.
IMPL - is the implementation of the API, provides the OSGi service.
SNAP - The Web Snap which uses the API to find the OSGi Service and presents a few simple web pages.


<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<plan name="sample.plan" version="1.0.0" scoped="true" atomic="true"
        xmlns="http://www.springsource.org/schema/dm-server/plan"
